gameRecap.title: Game Recap: Spurs 132, Thunder 118
gameRecap.excerpt: The Spurs defeated the Thunder, 132-118. Victor Wembanyama recorded 28 points (5-7 3PM), 13 rebounds, seven assists, and five blocks for the Spurs, with Devin Vassell adding 28 points and nine assists in the victory. Shai-Gilgeous Alexander tallied 31 points, six rebounds, and three assists for the Thunder in the losing effort. The Spurs improve to 12-48, while the Thunder fall to 41-18.
